-i am 'the little engine that could'...straight up
-i think i have worked myself into exhaustion/ strep throat

thats all.

I reported at my first national news event AND got exclusive footage that landed me the nickname, crouching tiger, hidden reporter. 

Tomorrow is the start of Fashion Week, time to put my freakum dress on.
